Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soaring Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Pace Hum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, a legendary samurai\Nwielded the great sword Shusui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure this katana would be\Nhappy to have you as its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your sword, but I'll pretend\Nthat our duel never happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...samurai of the Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chopper Is Furious!!\NHogback's Evil Medical Practices!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me: How does it feel to be\Nsubjugated by the might of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you tried to stuff salt\Ndown my throat with your weird powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I never expected \NSanji to kick Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't Sanji anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that Sanji guy?\NDon't make me kill you, jerk face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid they don't have a single\Nmemory of your days as crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Occasionally fresh zombies retain\Nsome of the shadow's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but these shadows have\Nfully settled into their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've completely lost their human hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've become zombies that\Nwill obey my every command!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as zombies are concerned,\Ntheir orders are absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually happy... to see that\Nyou're rotten to the core, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In all actuality, you have \Nsaved countless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did respect you as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for your zombie research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death can come suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are a lot \Nof things the deceased
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and those they left behind\Nnever got a chance to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking for years. If they\Ncould have just a few minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a way to bring back the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if people cast stones,\Ncalling it "evil medicine"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would mean the world to those it saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when you said that you were\Nresearching how to "resurrect the dead,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you truly\Nwere an amazing doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Why would I go to\Nsuch lengths for others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you respected how I used\Nto save lives, but it was the same deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I conducted operations for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was no stopping\Nthe unwanted flood of patients
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that came from around \Nthe world for treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save my dad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save my child!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save my beloved!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got old!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The run-of-the-mill quack\Ncouldn't save them, but I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you understand the hardships of a genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to respect me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your disappointment is uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't forgive me as a doctor\Nbecause I don't match your ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you never understood me\Nto begin with, stupid reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to start\Nlecturing me on medical ethics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't dream of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't consider you a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for these zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you've done is reanimate the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take life so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be rather cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving right before your very eyes,\Nand you think they aren't alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chopper, the "dead" are being given\Na second shot at life. It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you want to reject these lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now start licking the floor, Cindry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hogback-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see that room, Dr. Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The numerous photos were of the stage\Nactress Victoria Cindry before she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been in love with \Nher for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one. Her beauty had\Ncharmed men from across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all set, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry! I shouldn't make a\Npatient sew a button back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'll be \Nable to go back on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother! Sorry to \Nhave kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite her popularity, \Nshe was down to earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was close to her family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was kind to everyone...\NA truly wonderful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rejected my proposal, \Nwhen my renown as a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had let me obtain anything I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She already had a fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And shortly thereafter, I caught wind\Nof some news that left me dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry had died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ultimately abandoned my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is when he came.\NA giant man appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my master, Gecko Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Hogback, lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I boarded this ship under the condition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he would use his miraculous\Nability to resurrect Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so easy to obtain the actress,\NCindry, and bend her to my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish plates would cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The personality of the woman who had\Nspurned me was of little consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she retained her beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the zombie, Cindry-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm thrilled,\Nbut I'm sure she is as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gets to live in this \Nworld as a human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call her a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:14:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make her stop licking the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a human's heart isn't linked\Nto her body, she is no longer human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using corpses that can't\Nstick up for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're creating nothing but monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every zombie you create,\Nyou're making a person miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that out, which is\Nwhy I can't forgive you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lecture me on life when you're\Na mediocre doctor, pirate reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry-chan, finish those two off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn you guys into marios!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice, Dr. Chopper! Once you are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you my assistant,\Nsince you admire me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Square Plate Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate her\Njust because she's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've enhanced her muscles for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to listen to\Nthat monster! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing! And here you're already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would the family you left behind\Nfeel if they knew about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your family saw you covered in stitches
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and being used as an expendable soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would tear them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart you were born and\Nraised with is already dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your body is being forced\Nto do the bidding of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you questioning your eyes? Face facts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mankind's eternal dream!\NI've resurrected the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dead can come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the ability to move all that matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are freer than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who treats them\Nlike they aren't humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, hurry and feed her salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogguin! Jigoro! Help Cindry out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take out the pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...108-Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doce Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not... her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take out... the pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Jerk!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack me along\Nwith them?! Don't be a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pests are supposed to get taken outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get going! He issued that order to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was meant for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said he issued it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:19:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, knock it off! You \Nneed to actually work--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this turning out to be fascinating?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ordered them to "take out the pests."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are obediently trying to\Nobey that order even as I speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what would happen\Nif you didn't issue a new order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without their memories,\Nthose two are still like water and oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:20:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a rather tall tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you order the two\Nof us to jump out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say that as many times as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump! Jump! I want you to\Njump out the window together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sure.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run faster! He wants us to jump out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me! You're horrible!\NYou're the scum of all mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy will purify all of the\Nzombies when he defeats Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I want to throttle, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Cindry! Buy me some time!\NI'm gonna run for the hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my answer? I'll give you\Nanother shadow if they take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cindry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now you get to meet him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge! This is my shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he has finally decided to submit to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me: Who is your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master is Moria-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oars Roars! Come Out, Straw Hat Crew!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
